That's the worst thing about isolation.</i>

715
01:24:12,386 --> 01:24:16,345
<i>The clear knowledge that one
does not have a chance of survival.</i>

716
01:24:24,826 --> 01:24:28,375
Today we begin a hunger strike.

717
01:24:28,506 --> 01:24:32,055
We demand change to
one of the prison conditions:

718
01:24:32,386 --> 01:24:37,540
Equal conditions for political
prisoners to all other prisoners.

719
01:24:38,386 --> 01:24:42,345
A hunger strike is our only way...

720
01:24:42,546 --> 01:24:46,380
to resist in solitary confinement.

721
01:24:49,586 --> 01:24:52,544
<i>The hunger strike is to show</i>

722
01:24:52,746 --> 01:24:57,297
<i>that we will not compromise.</i>

723
01:24:57,906 --> 01:25:02,900
<i>We expect explosions
in the prison system.</i>

724
01:25:05,106 --> 01:25:09,065
<i>The goals must be
set out so that each Rocker,</i>

725
01:25:09,266 --> 01:25:13,225
<i>so everyone, does not
lose their sense of purpose.</i>

726
01:25:13,346 --> 01:25:16,895
<i>That is, so that
they do not break us.</i>

727
01:25:18,186 --> 01:25:23,306
<i>We can say: Each 3rd week,
or each 2nd or 4th week, whatever...</i>

728
01:25:24,026 --> 01:25:26,859
<i>one of us will die.</i>

729
01:25:27,186 --> 01:25:29,905
<i>And so on, until the isolation,</i>

730
01:25:30,026 --> 01:25:33,860
<i>until the torture for all is waived.</i>

731
01:25:35,266 --> 01:25:40,545
<i>But the hunger strike will only work
