733
01:25:56,226 --> 01:26:01,175
Counsellor, just a few minutes.
The prisoner is very much weakened.

734
01:26:08,266 --> 01:26:11,224
Gudrun wrote to me.

735
01:26:17,746 --> 01:26:22,866
This is our goal. You decide it,
when you die. Freedom or death.

736
01:26:23,826 --> 01:26:28,138
Just in case,
if I pass from this life,

737
01:26:29,866 --> 01:26:32,426
It's murder.

738
01:26:34,226 --> 01:26:39,175
If the pigs keep this up, it's murder.
Do not believe the lies of murderers.

739
01:26:49,186 --> 01:26:51,746
Get me a cigarette.

740
01:27:00,986 --> 01:27:04,945
<i>I don't know what will
happen, I should die.</i>

741
01:27:05,706 --> 01:27:08,539
<i>If I'm killed.</i>

742
01:27:09,946 --> 01:27:12,506
<i>What next?</i>

743
01:27:17,706 --> 01:27:19,458
<i>That's it.</i>

744
01:27:21,066 --> 01:27:24,024
<i>Which side is right?</i>

745
01:27:26,586 --> 01:27:29,419
<i>It's not so clear.</i>

746
01:27:30,666 --> 01:27:35,820
<i>The final battle to free
mankind from the pigs.</i>

747
01:27:38,106 --> 01:27:40,939
<i>The revolutionary struggle.</i>

748
01:27:43,146 --> 01:27:47,537
<i>With love for life
and with contempt for death.</i>

749
01:27:50,106 --> 01:27:53,462
<i>I serve the people.</i>

750
01:27:59,746 --> 01:28:04,024
Get the prison doctor here, now.
