- We don't have one.

752
01:28:08,306 --> 01:28:12,345
Then call in an outside doctor.
- We're not authorized.

753
01:28:12,466 --> 01:28:17,017
He's dying in there!
Get a doctor! Now!

754
01:28:18,066 --> 01:28:21,024
Unfortunately, we can't do a thing.

755
01:28:59,506 --> 01:29:03,340
One day after the death of Holger Meins,

756
01:29:03,666 --> 01:29:08,694
of the Baader-Meinhof Group,
who died while on hunger strike,

757
