828
01:37:01,906 --> 01:37:06,457
Why do you change my notes
suddenly, without explanation?

829
01:37:06,626 --> 01:37:11,780
Because that things
you write have no power.

830
01:37:13,146 --> 01:37:16,104
There's no need to do that.

831
01:37:19,106 --> 01:37:23,657
You jump on my errors
and go on and on about it.

832
01:37:24,546 --> 01:37:29,700
I could write a book on
your foolishness. Guard!

833
01:37:30,106 --> 01:37:33,940
Your tired act,
I'm sick of it.

834
01:37:34,306 --> 01:37:38,822
I've had my fill of this.
You're driving me crazy!

835
01:37:44,146 --> 01:37:47,104
Really, I don't get it.

836
01:37:47,346 --> 01:37:50,304
What's their problem, the bitches?

837
01:37:50,466 --> 01:37:54,744
It's the last straw that
they allowed Hausner to die.

838
01:37:54,866 --> 01:37:58,825
