842
01:38:12,906 --> 01:38:15,739
Not a clue! Piss off!

843
01:38:17,946 --> 01:38:20,779
Piss off, arsehole!

844
01:38:21,346 --> 01:38:24,179
Get us out of here, you sow!

845
01:38:24,626 --> 01:38:27,186
Get us out of here!

846
01:38:28,026 --> 01:38:30,586
Sow! Arsehole!

847
01:38:30,786 --> 01:38:33,300
Get us out of here, you sow!

848
01:38:51,786 --> 01:38:56,177
Mrs Meinhof, you are obliged to remain.
