has no other chance.

892
01:43:59,986 --> 01:44:03,945
So there are two possibilities.

893
01:44:04,186 --> 01:44:08,657
I will speak now!
A prisoner can be silent,

894
01:44:08,786 --> 01:44:12,904
and die,
or a prisoner can talk.

895
01:44:13,026 --> 01:44:17,975
